@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "You Social Butterfly, you";
    ViewBag.MetaDescription = "We provide social media content creation services for brands that want remarkable results from their media investments.";
}

<section class="section">
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12 text-center">
				<img src="~/images/logo/brand-brandmark-color.svg" height="60px">
				<h1 class="display-1 mt-4">@ViewData["Title"]...🔥</h1>
				<div class="max-width mx-auto mt-4">
					<div class="">We provide <b>social media content</b> creation services for brands that want remarkable results from their media investments.</div>
				</div>
				<a href="https://calendly.com/brandflex/branding?utm_source=website&utm_medium=button&utm_campaign=social_content" target="_blank" class="btn btn-black mt-4 gtm-social-call"><i class="fas fa-headset mr-2"></i>Upgrade your Social Media<span> game</span></a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>


<section class="process">
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
				<div class="card bg-light no-shadow">
					<div class="card-body text-dark">
						<h4>1. Discovery</h4>
						<p class="">You get a clear understanding of how your company’s goals and audience’s needs can be met with compelling social media content.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
            </div>
           <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
				<div class="card bg-light no-shadow">
					<div class="card-body text-dark">
                    	<h4>2. Architecture</h4>
                    	<p class="">You get a social media content blueprint that defines your content themes of focus with concrete examples and concepts.</p>
					</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
				<div class="card bg-light no-shadow last">
					<div class="card-body text-dark">
                    	<h4>3. Content</h4>
						<p class="">You get monthly batches of content or we create a guide to do it yourself that’s customised for your goals and channels.</p>
					</div>
                </div>
            </div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>



<section class="section">
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row align-items-center">
			<div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
				<h2 class="display-2">Instagram</h2>
				<p class="lead">Picture your company.</p>

				<p>People come to Instagram to capture a moment in time and relive that memory in the future. They learn, laugh, dream and raise their voice, so your Instagram content strategy needs to be thoughtful.</p> 
				
				<p class="lead">Consider the formats:</p>
				<ul class="fa-ul">
					<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fad fa-check text-primary"></i></span>Short-form vertical Stories with their own creative language</li>
					<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fad fa-check text-primary"></i></span>Feed posts that form cohesive brand grids</li>
					<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fad fa-check text-primary"></i></span>Live and longer video you can replay later (IGTV)</li>
				</ul>
				<p>With your input, we’ll create eye-catching stories and posts that are worth a thousand words.</p>
				<a href="https://calendly.com/brandflex/branding?utm_source=website&utm_medium=button&utm_campaign=instagram" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary mt-4"><i class="fas fa-headset mr-2"></i>Book a Free <span>Instagram</span> Call</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4 ml-auto hidden-md-down">
				<ul id="sceneI" class="scene mt-5"
					data-friction-x="0.4"
					data-friction-y="0.4"
					data-scalar-x="30"
					data-scalar-y="30">
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.10"><div class="splash1"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.20"><div class="splash2"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.30"><div class="ig I"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.40"><div class="ig II"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.50"><div class="ig III"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.60"><div class="heart-left"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.70"><div class="heart-right"></div></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="section pt-0">
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row align-items-center">
			<div class="col-md-4 hidden-md-down">
				<ul id="sceneII" class="scene mt-5"
					data-friction-x="0.4"
					data-friction-y="0.4"
					data-scalar-x="30"
					data-scalar-y="30">
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.10"><div class="splash1"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.20"><div class="splash2"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.30"><div class="fb I"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.40"><div class="fb II"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.50"><div class="fb III"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.60"><div class="like-left"></div></li>
					<li class="layer" data-depth="0.70"><div class="like-right"></div></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6 ml-auto">
				<h2 class="display-2">Facebook</h2>
				<p class="lead">Keep fans in the loop.</p>
				<p>Platforms come and go. Facebook has lasting power. We can help you get friendly with your Facebook supporters using organic content that still earns reach—like live streams, personal video, and events.</p>
				<p class="lead">Consider the formats:</p>
				<ul class="fa-ul">
					<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fad fa-check text-primary"></i></span>Images in post styles</li>
					<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fad fa-check text-primary"></i></span>Video for adding movement to your ads</li>
					<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fad fa-check text-primary"></i></span>Live and longer video you can replay later (IGTV)</li>
				</ul>
				<p>Is your presence mostly paid? No problem.We have been designing Facebook ads for 8 years and can skip right to the top-performing formats and elements.</p>
				<a href="https://calendly.com/brandflex/branding?utm_source=website&utm_medium=button&utm_campaign=facebook" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary mt-4"><i class="fas fa-headset mr-2"></i>Book a Free <span>Facebook</span> Call</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="section pt-0">
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-5">
				<h2 class="display-2">LinkedIn</h2>
				<p class="lead">Take your audience seriously.</p>

				<p>LinkedIn is where it gets a bit serious, and your followers are talking about climbing the proverbial career ladder. Content should elevate your work status, solve people problems, and earns their trust. LinkedIn is build to  handle the business side of things. We can help put your content's tie on for this one.</p>
				<a href="https://calendly.com/brandflex/branding?utm_source=website&utm_medium=button&utm_campaign=linkedin" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary mt-4"><i class="fas fa-headset mr-2"></i>Book a Free <span>LinkedIn</span> Call</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-5 ml-auto">
				<h2 class="display-2">Twitter</h2>
				<p class="lead">Start a conversation.</p>

				<p>It is quirky, it is direct and it is a conversation starter. Twitter has all the ingredients of poking at a topic or raising your inner voice. Together, we’ll create a voice, find your niche, and produce content that starts a conversation. One that can change the course of your brand.</p>
				<a href="https://calendly.com/brandflex/branding?utm_source=website&utm_medium=button&utm_campaign=twitter" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary mt-4"><i class="fas fa-headset mr-2"></i>Book a Free <span>Twitter</span> Call</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>



